    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Any patient with documented OSAHS who is scheduled for tongue base resection at UAB

          2. Age &gt; 19

          3. Patients must sign informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Psychological condition that renders the patient unable to understand the informed
             consent

          2. Any situation or condition that will interfere with adherence to study activities
      </textblock>
